{"tid":1834952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［求你入嚟幫推］有狗想喺粉嶺租倉伏手足！！！","createTime":"2020-01-22T15:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T16:17:29.000Z","uid":136663,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e5f1406cb716b2cff66363973975b7d31dc8385b","tid":1834952,"uid":136663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Djh66t8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjh66t8.jpg&h=490cc38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我有個深藍深紅親戚話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日有狗上嚟想租呢間公司嘅倉，話係去伏示威者</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰個親戚話佢拒絕咗，但我唔係好信，同埋啲狗極有可能同區搵其他地方問<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個地點近粉嶺火車站</span></span>，我唔知報上邊度好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果覺得有價值可唔可以幫我輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c14995ca4b7cfdc00e0d445cde9a82b76340e0f","tid":1834952,"uid":136663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a8e7f839bdd2eaf9d507411910f99b41fbd477","tid":1834952,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"安樂村唔算近啦吓嘛"},{"pid":"e888a46241904d161d83e1630c7d2b795fed8ac1","tid":1834952,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:37:22.000Z